org.eclipse.scada.vi.model

Interface SymbolReference

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Primitive
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SymbolReferenceImpl

    public interface SymbolReference
extends Primitive
    A representation of the model object 'Symbol Reference'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Uri
    • Zoom
    • Properties
    • On Create Properties

    See Also:
    VisualInterfacePackage.getSymbolReference()
